    "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><br>\nAn <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"b6f60f2f331c5ad04e19a91d0ba388f4\">IMO</span> process whereby navigation system providers submit their systems for recognition. The requirements and procedures for acceptance are set out in <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"b6f60f2f331c5ad04e19a91d0ba388f4\">IMO</span> Resolution <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"7fc56270e7a70fa81a5935b72eacbe29\">A</span>.953(23).\n</p><p><br>\nSource: Nick Ward, Vicechair, <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> e-Nav Committee, March 2009\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"b6f60f2f331c5ad04e19a91d0ba388f4\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Maritime Organization\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"7fc56270e7a70fa81a5935b72eacbe29\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>ampere\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div clas